https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Karol-G-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Karol-G-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Karol-G-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Karol-G">Karol G</a>宣布她将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>合作于 2025 年发行一部纪录片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/karol-g-manana-sera-bonito-bichota-season-review-3481832">Karol G – “Mañana Será Bonito（Bichota Season）”评论：她的统治仍在继续</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据流媒体巨头今天（12 月 30 日）发布的一条推文，一部涵盖哥伦比亚巨星生活和职业生涯的纪录片将于明年上线。据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/karol-g-netflix-documentary-feature-1235866760/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《公告牌》</em></a>报道，艾美奖获奖导演兼制片人克里斯蒂娜·科斯坦蒂尼将执导该项目。</p><p> Karol G 在她的 Instagram 官方账户上与粉丝们分享了这一消息，其中附有一张纸条照片，上面写着：“一个故事诞生于看似不可能的梦想，由坚定不移的信念推动。这是一次克服一切困难的不懈旅程。</p><p> “我的生活、我的工作、我的真理以及我与大家分享的强大联系。我的梦想实现了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DENOiqvOHkH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"